Subject: dt-bindings: clk: qcom: ipq9574: add WCSS Q6 clocks

Add the IPQ9574 GCC clock IDs needed by the native WCSS remoteproc
bring-up path. These clocks are used by qcom_q6v5_wcss when booting the
integrated Wi-Fi firmware outside PAS mode.

Signed-off-by: Alexandru Gagniuc <mr.nuke.me@gmail.com>
Signed-off-by: Igor Kravchenko <igor.kravchenko05@gmail.com>
